{
  "stem": "5551.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] While before the war, they were not all that kind, as the war went on and as more and more Polish suffered the-- the indignities and the rest of-- of the German murderers, they developed a certain alliance with the Jews, at that time, at that period of time.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This goes back to this man in the forest who aided us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I will go back to the story that I eye-witnessed about about Otto Friedrich, the chief of the Gestapo in Gorlice, because I already mentioned his name.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I mentioned the name of my uncle, Janusz Keller.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was babysitting his child-- by the way, he and his whole family were murdered.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But-- but at the time, I believe it was 19-- it was early 1942.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It could have been late in '41.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But the windows of my uncle's apartment looked down at a Polish retention tank of the Polish police.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They had a retention tank there that they used for Polish people who got drunk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They-- they put them in there until they sobered up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I was babysitting my cousin, my little cousin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It got late.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we were not permitted to be in the street after dark, so I stayed overnight there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I slept by the window that looked into that backyard of the Polish police, with that retention tank.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I was awakened, after midnight, by bright light and the sound of a motorcycle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "When I looked down, I saw Otto Friedrich, the chief of the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He was in his shiny boots and white gloves on a motorcycle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Apparently, the Polish police had found eight Gypsy children in a-- in a forest nearby.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It could've been the same forest-- probably was-- where we were hiding.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
